TxnEventType
If the event returned in the response is a transaction event, this field contains the type of transaction involved in the event.

Values:
ARRefundCreditCard, Bill, BillPaymentCheck, BillPaymentCreditCard, Charge, Check, CreditCardCharge, CreditCardCredit, CreditMemo, Deposit, Estimate, InventoryAdjustment, Invoice, ItemReceipt, JournalEntry, PurchaseOrder, ReceivePayment, SalesOrder, SalesReceipt, SalesTaxPaymentCheck, TimeTracking, VendorCredit

No default value.
